'''布賴特靈西'''（Brightlingsea）是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]的一個海濱城鎮。據2011年英國人口普查，布賴特靈西有人口8,076人<ref name = ONS>{{cite web |url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11121186&c=Brightlingsea&d=16&e=62&g=6425845&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1440961043320&enc=1 |title=Key Figures for 2011 Census: Brightlingsea |publisher=Office for National Statistics (Neighbourhood Statistics) |accessdate=30 August 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095339/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11121186&c=Brightlingsea&d=16&e=62&g=6425845&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1440961043320&enc=1 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。當地的主要產業是漁業。
